<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cloud Infrastructure - {{ environment }}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{ gradient_start | default('#667eea') }} 0%, {{ gradient_end | default('#764ba2') }} 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            padding: 50px;
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: {{ gradient_start | default('#667eea') }};
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .environment-badge {
            background: {{ gradient_end | default('#764ba2') }};
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .info-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .value {
            color: {{ gradient_start | default('#667eea') }};
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .tech-stack {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .tech-badge {
            background: {{ gradient_start | default('#667eea') }};
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .status {
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .feature-list {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .feature-list h3 {
            color: #0066cc;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .feature-list ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .deployment-info {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .deployment-info strong {
            color: #856404;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üöÄ {{ project_name | default('Cloud Infrastructure') }}</h1>
        <div class="center">
            <span class="environment-badge">{{ environment }} Environment</span>
        </div>
        <p class="subtitle">Automated Deployment with Terraform & Ansible</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Environment:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ environment }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Server Hostname:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ ansible_hostname }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Public IP:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Private IP:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Operating System:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Kernel Version:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ ansible_kernel }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Deployment Date:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ ansible_date_time.date }} {{ ansible_date_time.time }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="label">Deployed By:</span>
                <span class="value">Ansible</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-list">
            <h3>üìä Infrastructure Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Infrastructure as Code:</strong> Terraform managed AWS resources</li>
                <li><strong>Configuration Management:</strong> Ansible role-based setup</li>
                <li><strong>Multi-Environment:</strong> Separate dev, staging, and prod configs</li>
                <li><strong>High Availability:</strong> VPC with public subnet and internet gateway</li>
                <li><strong>Security:</strong> Security groups with least privilege access</li>
                <li><strong>Monitoring:</strong> CloudWatch logs and metrics integration</li>
                <li><strong>CI/CD:</strong> Automated deployment via GitHub Actions</li>
                <li><strong>Scalability:</strong> Modular architecture for easy scaling</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="deployment-info">
            <strong>‚ÑπÔ∏è Deployment Method:</strong> 
            This server was configured using Ansible playbook with the 'webserver' role.
            All configurations are version-controlled and reproducible.
        </div>

        <div class="tech-stack">
            <span class="tech-badge">Terraform</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Ansible</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">AWS EC2</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Nginx</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">CloudWatch</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">GitHub Actions</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Ubuntu 22.04</span>
        </div>

        <p class="status center">‚úÖ Successfully Deployed via Ansible Role!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
